# cratedig needs NO credentials — MusicBrainz is a free, keyless API.
# There is nothing required to configure here.
#
# Optionally, set any of these non-secret defaults (or use the equivalent CLI flags).
# Copy this file to ".env" and uncomment what you want to change. See DESIGN.md §9.
#
# OUTPUT_DIR=/path/to/your/music
# AUDIO_FORMAT=mp3
# BITRATE=192
# MAX_WORKERS=3
# COOKIES_FROM_BROWSER=firefox
